      • recalculateTableBounds

        public void recalculateTableBounds(Board board)
        Recalculates the first row, first column, canvas width in table cells, canvas height in table cells, the half points on the table, number of columns and rows to display, and the panning bounds. This method is called whenever the canvas zooms or pans, or when the board has a pattern inserted or it resized.
        Parameters:
        board - The board to do all calculations relative to.
